com.kofhearts.safe.model

Class Entry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kofhearts.safe.model.ActiveRecord
      • com.kofhearts.safe.model.Entry

  • public class Entry
extends ActiveRecord
    Entry class represents an entry that is defined by three properties namely id, title and content. For example: An entry can be a bank account information in which case the title can be Bank Account Number and content can be 123812673
